Ka seeriŋkar ŋa kaawtu pey aman: " Nun meendu isgig iŋ ŋaara. " Kar ŋa kaawtu pey aman: " Taloŋ, nun ko kuuk Buŋ beriidu-aŋ iŋ kooginay. "
Hiyya, koogin-ak, taar tee iŋ baarco, ŋuur sa tee ziŋkico di. Kar Iisa gay, wiktin taat ŋa rakiyco aawe, ŋa gaasiig ŋuur kuuk gin gudurre, asaan iŋ muutco ŋa rakiy deen̰ji, ŋaar kaak gin gudurre, ŋaar seetanne.
Ŋa iyin̰co min ɗo gee kuuk kolaw ku muut-ak, asaan ɗo goyin̰co okin̰co, ŋu gina ziŋkico ɓerrina asaan ŋu gina kolaw ar muut-aka.
Sando, ka seener gay, ŋa bal obin̰ *ɗubal ku Buŋdi, kar gay, ŋa obin̰ roŋ ku tamba ta Ibraayim.
Ɗo saan taar-at ko, Iisa yaa gine ar siŋtay iŋ gamin okin̰co. Paa kat, ŋa asiy gine *mee satkiner ka tatko kaak tala aminduwiy ho kaak sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Paa kat, ŋaa gine saamiye ɗo zunuubinnar ka geemir.
Ka seener gay, Iisa meen̰ji sa, ŋa iban kadar Buŋ meen̰ji di gedirgiy gecin̰ji, ŋa gediraaɗo ŋaa coole gee kuuk gecaag gecen di.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gem kol siŋtay kuuk aamin ɗo Buŋdi ho kuuk Buŋ koliig iŋ kuŋko oki, ibinoŋ Iisa Masi kaak ku obtu kaaw taat ku astu ho ŋaar ko *mee satkiner ka tatko.
Ŋa aamintu ɗo Buŋdi ar kaak Muusa gintu riy ɗo geriy. Iŋ taar-at oki, Muusa obiig riy ta Buŋdi ɗo geriy.
Ka seener gay, Buŋ berji *darjin pakgig Muusa. Ho gem kaak pinig ger-ak, ŋaar gas darjin pakgig ger kaak tatik pakgig ger ka Buŋdi okin̰ji.
Asaan ay ger kat gin gem di pinigji, kar gay, ŋaar kaak pinig gamin okin̰co-ak, ŋa Buŋ.
Muusa gay aamintu ɗo Buŋdi. Ŋa gin gudurre pakgig gamin okin̰co ku geriy okin̰co. Ŋa kaawiy seen ta Buŋdi ho Buŋ kaawtu kadar gamin okin̰co kuuk Buŋ kaawtu-ak yaa kuuniye.
Kar Masi gay, ŋaar ar roŋ kat gooƴa ɗo adiy ka gerdi. Gamin ku gerdi-aŋ, ŋuur kuuk ni goyiy di, illa gii icin kaaw taat ni diytu malle ho taat ni pakira ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Ansii ko, diŋka-aŋ, ya ku cokiyiit gaaƴ ta Buŋdi, ar taat Ruwwin ta Buŋdi kaawiico aman: " Ƴiriyta ya ku cokiyiit gaaƴ ta Buŋdi,
Iisa gaayiitit ɗo kaawoy aman: " Dakoŋ un̰jenno kaƴko ar ŋu *Seetanne teestu meele. Ƴiriy taar-at ko, ŋu geciig Buŋ ɗo goosiner.
Awalle, aginiyko gay gecintu, ŋu taaɓiyindu, asaan ŋu talig maan kaak nu gintu.
" Gee ku diŋka-aŋ, ŋuur goy ko elgin orok pooɗ. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, nu awn̰iig gee ku diŋka ho nu ɗiytu aman: ‟ Zulin̰co ŋu rawte kaƴco, ŋu rawte botol taat nu gintu. "
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, wiktin taat nu gintu riy ɗo riy ta Buŋdi-ak, nu indiig aman: ‟ Ha'a, ŋu un̰jaaɗo un̰je ɗo wer kaak nu ɓaawtu jammiye! "
Ampa-ak, gem kol siŋtay, yaman pakiroŋ, ya minninko rakki gin gelbinko samaane ho imaanji bombo, kuu rasin̰ Buŋ kaak goy mento.
Kar gay, kun kawta, min ƴiriy taat ŋu goyiy misa ƴiriy taat gee kolaag ‟ ‟ Ƴiriy ta ƴiriy " di, diyoŋ bombo rakki minninko gediraaɗo ɗeŋrin̰co iŋ zunuubinna,
Ka seener gay, okinte, ni ween̰ciŋ iŋ Masi. Ni talig iŋ ŋaara, gee kuuk asa mate, ŋuu mate nam nii gaase duniin okintiti.
Ampaa ko, ɗo Kitamner, Buŋ kaawtu aman: " Ƴiriyta-aŋ ya ku cokiya gaaƴay ta Buŋdi, dakoŋ ɗeŋginno kaƴko bombo ar ŋu newsiig aditko. "
Ya ŋu dorit kaaw ta Buŋdi-at, maa di ŋu dapin̰tu aale? Ha'a, ŋuur okin̰co kuuk Muusa gaartu min Meser-ak ɗoo di!
Ku iban kadar Iisa taltu ko elgin orok pooɗ ɗo elginar-ak gay maman? Gee-ak bal nige zunuubinna walla? Ha'a, ŋuur kuuk bal eeze ɗo goosiner!
Ansii ko, Buŋ ɗiytu pey aman: ‟ Waa yaa un̰je ɗo wer kaak ŋa beriijiɗo Buŋ? Ha'a, ginno. Ŋuur kuuk bal aamine bal un̰je. "
Hiyya, ni tala kadar ŋu bal gedire un̰je ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi asaan ŋu bal aamine ɗo Iisa Masi. "
Ŋa kaawtu pa-ak, illa gii gase kolaw. Yampa, maan kaak ŋa kaawtu a ŋaa un̰je ɗo goye kaak ŋa beriico oki. Ŋa ginno kolaw paa di, ya minninko rakki minninko rakki ni gediraaɗo un̰je.
Ka seener gay, ni gaarinti Kabarre ta Gala ɗo gee kuuk goy anne-aŋku. Kar kaaw taat ŋu dortu-at balco gaaye caari, asaan ŋu bal icin kaaw-at ɗo uŋco ka imaanco.
Ka seener gay, gee kuuk aamine, gi ɓaa un̰je ɗo wer kaak Buŋ kaawtu awalle a ŋuu un̰je ɗo goye kaak ŋa rakiyo. Ka seener gay, gee-ak yaa un̰je ɗo wer kaak ŋa un̰jitu gine ar taat ŋa gintu min Buŋ kilgiyiit duniine. Iŋ taar-at ko, Buŋ kaawtu awalle aman: " Gii un̰je koɗok di, ŋuu un̰je ɗo wer kaak nu ɓaay jammiye.
Ɗo bi ka Abdi-ak ko, Buŋ kaawtu pey aman: " Ƴiriy rakki, Buŋ weƴtu min ɗo riy okintiti taat ŋa gintu. "
Ɗo wer ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ kaawtu pey aman: " Ha'a, ŋu gediraaɗo un̰je ɗo wer kaak nu un̰jitu pey ɗo goyin̰ji! "
Ansii ko, gee kuuk awalle gaartu Kabarre ta Gala bal un̰je ɗo geegirdi asaan ŋu poocit kaawco. Kar daarin̰ gay, ŋu un̰jitu ɗo geegirdi asaan ŋu rakaaɗo un̰je.
Kar Buŋ ɗiytu pey aman: " Ƴiriyta! " Ŋa doɓtu pey ƴiriy rakki taat Buŋ kaawtu min awalle ɗo Dawuud min daayum. Ŋa kaawtu pey aman: " Ƴiriy taar-an, ya ku cokiyiit gaaƴar, dakoŋ ɗibirinno gelbinko bombo.
Ka seener gay, min ƴiriy taar-at, Iisa bal amile misa ho ŋa bal kaawe pey baati.
Ansii ko, Buŋ gintu ƴiriy rakki ta sabitdi ɗo gee ku Buŋdi.
Asaan ya gem kaak un̰jitu ɗo riyoy ɗo Buŋdi, ŋaar oki weƴtu min ɗo riy okintit taat ŋa gintu. Iŋ taar-at ko, Buŋ etirtu min ɗo riy okintit taat ŋa rakiyo.
Di ŋaar-ak, indoŋ ja, gii un̰je koɗok ɗo goye kaak ŋa rakiyo. Yampa, paa kat, gee kuuk pooc-ak sa aaɗiyɗo pey sooɗa.
Ka seener gay, kaaw ta Buŋdi, taar goy mento ho ta gin gudurre. Ta taar pakgig pakgig ay seepinpan kaak awalle. Ta taar-at un̰jaaɗo nam ta eergig keɗer, ta eergig kelmoy iŋ ruwwine. Ta asaaco gaare baat ta pikirre ta geemir ho iŋ pikirre ta aditco.
Ŋa talaagɗo gamin okin̰co kuuk cigile. Gamin okin̰co, ŋu tukinka, ŋu caaltu tak-tak ɗo uŋji. Ŋa gaarintiŋ ko imaanke.
Gem kaak gin mee satkiner ka tatko kaak tatiko kaak jaaw min kuwa ka Buŋdi, ŋa Iisa, Roŋ ka Buŋdi. Diŋ gay, obig kaaw-an bombo ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Ka seener, ni ginno *mee satkiner ka tatko kaak ibanno aminduwte kaak taaɓiyaate. Ŋaar gay, ŋaar as gaase ɗo ay maanna, kar gay, ŋa bal gine zunuubinna.
Di ŋaar-ak, gi ɓaaŋgu iŋ gelbin rakki ɗo sees ka Buŋdi iŋ gelbin rakki. Gi ɓaa gase barkin min ɗo Buŋdi ho gii gase barkin taat ŋaa gase gaayo ɗo wiktin taat yaa nece.
Ka seener gay, gem rakki goy mee satkiner ka tatko, ŋaar di goy ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ɗo bi ka gee okin̰co. Ŋa giniy *satkin ɗo Buŋdi, ŋaa gine *satkin ɗo uŋji ho ŋaa gine *satkin ɗo bi ka zunuubinnar.
Ŋa karmiyaag gee kuuk ibanno maanna ho ŋu rawtaag ŋuur kuuk rawte. Ŋaar gay raɗaw oki.
Kar iŋ taar-at, ta mataaɗo ar taat ta mattu ɗo bi ka gee okin̰co. Ansii ko, ta giniy *satkine ɗo bi ka meen̰ji, ŋaa gase saamiye ɗo zunuubinnico. "
Ya ɗo tan̰ji-at, ŋaar meen̰jiɗo kat gasaagɗo oziliik ta geemir-aka. Kar gay, ŋaar kaak Buŋ kat koltu, ŋaar kat bergiy oziliik ta geemir-aka, ŋaar iŋ *Haruun.
Ansii ko, Masi oki, ŋaar balji berin pey barkin ɗo ziy a ŋaa gine mee satkiner ka tatko. Ŋaar kat kaawji ɗo Buŋ kaak kaawiiji aman: " Kiŋke-aŋ ko Roŋdu, min ƴiriyta-aŋ, nun ko Takko. "
Ɗo wer ka pey, ɗo wer ka pey, Buŋ kaaw aman: " Kiŋ goy *mee satkiner ka gaasɗo ar *mee satkiner kaak Melsi-Lebi. "
Ɗo wiktin taat ŋa goyiy misa ɗo duniiner, ŋu ooyiiga ho ŋu salkiyiiga ɗo uŋji ka Buŋ kaak gin gudurre kaak nec iye muutuy. Zuudas, ŋa alaw iŋ taaɓine ho iŋ zulin̰ji oki, ŋu ooyiiga. Kar Buŋ sa taliig iŋ uŋji ka Buŋdi asaan ŋa elgig dakina.
Kar ŋa weetu roŋji, ŋaar rawte min ɗo duniiner.
Kar iŋ taar-at oki, ta galtu ɗo gee kuuk cokiyaaga a ŋuu gase jile ka gaasɗo ɗo gee okin̰co kuuk cokiyaaga.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ doɓtu a ŋaar ko *mee satkiner ka tatko ar kaak *Melkidi-Batist.
" Ɗo bi kaŋko, nu gin kaawin dakina kuuk ƴiriy rakki diŋka. Kaawin ŋuur-ak ɗeŋginko samaane ho ku bal poocin̰coɗo. Ucoŋ, cokiyon kaawin-an samaane!
Ya ku taliy-aŋ, min diŋka-aŋ, ku iban kadar ku ɓildaako gee. Kar diŋ gay, ku ibanno pey gem kaak yaako ɓildiŋko baati ta kaawin kuuk taɓ ku Buŋdi teestu. Kuŋ gay ar gee kuuk gina ziŋkiko ar kaak ŋu siyaako misa, yampa, ku gin ar ŋuur kuuk gina ziŋkiko ar kaak patiis.
Ka seener, gem kaak tiya maam ku poddine, ŋaar ginaaɗo kaaw ta goye kaak sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Iŋ taar-at oki, ŋa ginaaɗo maam ku Buŋdi.
Kar gay, tee kaak tiyaw-ak gay, ŋaar tiyaw. Gee ŋuur-ak, ziŋkico goy ko iŋ aditco, ŋu gedarro gaare maan kaak samaane iŋ kaak samaanno.
Di ŋaar-ak, ni ictu kaaw taat ŋu kaawtu awalle ɗo bi ka Masi, kar ni ɓaayiy gaare kaaw taat gaay ko ote ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ni ictu niyine a nii ibinin̰ nigin̰co, ni rasin̰ goye kaak awalle min ɗo riy taat ŋu giniy min ɗo muuti, ho nii aamine ɗo Buŋdi.
Kaawin kuuk ŋu kaawtu ɗo gamin kuuk ŋu *batiziyiig gee ho kuuk ŋu garkiyiy pisin̰co ɗo kaƴco, ku mate asa nooye ho seriin ta Buŋdi yaa obin̰co tak-tak.
Ŋaar-ak gay, gi ginin̰ji ya Buŋ ber botol ho gii ginin̰ji. "
Ka seener gay, gee kuuk goy misa portikaw-ak, ŋu taltu maan kaak Buŋ beriico min kuwa ho ŋu gastu Ruwwin ta Buŋdi.
ho ansi-ak, ŋu ibingig samaane gamin kuuk Buŋ gintu gudurre tak-tak ɗo wiktin taat yaa ase.
ho ŋu poocit kaawoy. Ya ŋu gina pa-ak, ŋuu ibinin̰ pey a ŋuu ibinin̰ nigin̰co, ŋuu rasin̰ pey Roŋ ka Buŋdi ɗo ka etor. Iŋ taar-at ko, ŋu asiy ɗooɗin̰ ka etor ho ŋuu gine pey daŋla.
Ka seener gay, kiɗ kaak amiltu, ŋa maaɗtu, ŋa maaɗtu nam ŋa maaɗtu. Ŋa maaɗtu busam kuuk gee kuuk gooƴaag kiɗ-aka ho ŋaa coonin̰co. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ yaan̰ barkiyin̰ji.
Ta bite-aŋ di, ŋu amiltu ar buguwa, ŋu amiltu gulɓan̰-gulɓan̰ ho ŋu aaƴiig gaminco kuuk samaane. Gamin ŋuur-ak yaa nece nam koɗok di.
Ampa-ak, gem kol siŋtay, ya ni kaawa ampa-ak, taar isgicinno. Illa ŋaar-ak ko maan kaak Buŋ yaako jiliŋko. Yampa, ya gi kaawa ansi-ak, illa gii gase jile.
Asaan Buŋ, ŋaar ibanno maan kaak ŋa newsiikonno ɗo riy taat ku giniyo ho ɗo ele kaak ku gaartu ɗo bi kan̰ji. Ku gin riy taat samaane ɗo gee ku Buŋdi ho berko riy taar di.
Kar gay, ni raka kadar ay gemo minninko rakki gaare gudurre taat kuu obin̰ imaanko-anta nam ɗo muutuy.
Yampa, gi rakaaɗo peyin̰co tak-tak. Kar gay, ginoŋ ar ŋuur kuuk goy imaanco iŋ imaanco ho diŋka maala ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ŋuur gay yaa gase hagin taat Buŋ kaawtu a ŋaaji berin̰ji ɗo geemir.
Asaan wiktin taat Ibraayim doriit kaaw ta Buŋdi-at, ŋa bal ice kaawoy tak-tak. Iŋ taar-at oki, ŋa pakirtu kadar ginno gem kaak tatik pakgigɗo Buŋ.
ho ŋa kaawtu ɗo Buŋdi aman: ‟ Ya nu bal barkiyin̰ciŋ-ak, naan̰ barkiyin̰ciŋ ko dakina ho naan̰ miinin̰ciŋ pey dakina. "
Hiyya, ŋa bal taaye misa imaanco, kar ŋa gastu taat Buŋ kaawiico a ŋaaji ase ɗo geemir.
Ka seener gay, gee daarin̰ pakira a gee yaa gine tatik pakgig ŋuur kuuk tatik paka. Okin̰co, ŋuur isgigɗo maala ɗo uŋco ka geemir.
Buŋ ictu niyine a ŋaaco gaare pey waraŋ ɗo ŋuur kuuk yaa gase haginey taat ŋa kaawtu a ŋuu rasin̰ji tak-tak. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ŋa togiltu pey iŋ cigile.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Iisa Masi gaartu kaawinti ɗo geemir a gamin seer goy ɗatik ta Buŋdi. Iŋ taar-at oki, gee kuuk obit imaan taat ŋu diyiite ɗo uŋco ka geemir, gii obin̰ ja bombo bombo.
Taar ar mernan ku goy ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, taar as ni ɗuune ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ni gintenno kaƴni, ni gediraaɗo nige ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi nam ni un̰jaaɗo ɗo aki.
Ɗo wer-ak, Iisa gay ogirinti, ŋaar un̰jitu uŋte kaawoy. Ŋaar ko *mee satkiner ka tatko ar kaak Melsi-Lebi goyiy doo.
Gem-ak, siŋji Melsi-Lebi, ŋaar sultan ka Seleem ho ŋa gay satkiner ka Buŋ ka kuwa. Ɗo wiktin taat Ibraayim yeeptu min ŋa amil min ɗo sultinniidi ho ŋa yeepiyo, ŋa ɓaawtu barkiyin̰ji.
Min gee-ak okin̰co, Ibraayim weetu elgin orok. Ka seener, siŋ-ak awalle, ŋu kolaag a " Sultan kaak goy iŋ botol taat samaane. " Kar pey ŋa kolaag a " Sultan ka Salaaner. " Kar pey, ŋa kolaag a " Sultan ka aapiyer."
" Gem kol siŋji Teyopil, ŋaar bal ween̰ misa wee. Ŋaar bal ween̰ misa ween̰ji wala ŋa mattu. Kar gay, ŋaar Roŋ ka Buŋdi oki, ŋa goyaaɗo gay satkiner tak-tak.
Kar pakiroŋ ɗo kaƴko gay, gem-aŋ ŋaar kaak gas ko elgin orok seer min ɗo tambaay. Ibraayim, tatte Buŋ berji zakaane min ɗo kooginay ku Eglizdi.
" Ɗo *gaanuun ka Muusa kaawtu pey a gee ku Israyeel yaa gase zakaane ɗo *mee satkiner ku Lebi. Dawuud gay, ŋaar gay ɗiyiico ɗo *gaanuun a ŋaaco bere zakaane ɗo geemir. Siŋtay ar siŋta ku Lebi, ŋuur oki min tamba ta Ibraayim.
Min ŋuur-ak, siŋji Ibraayim nectu orok seer minninco ho ŋa barkiyiig ŋaar kaak gas ja kaaw taat Buŋ kaawtu a ŋaaji kaawe.
Nu kaawaako pey, ay gem kaak tiya bal baaco sa, Buŋ yaako barkiyiig mappa ka puusdi.
Ɗo wer-ak, goy gee orok iŋ bijigiƴ kuuk mate. Gee-ak obig samaane, kar gay, ŋu kaawiy biy iŋ odinay a ŋa goy mento.
Ɗo wer-ak, Buŋ kaawiy pey aman: ‟ Ŋaar kaak kappa orok-ak, ŋa kappiyiit orok-ak min ɗo Ibraayim iŋ Lebi. "
Ka seener gay, Melsi-Lebi gay goy iŋ odinay, asaan ŋa goy misa iŋ tambaay ta tacco Buŋ.
Ya gay satkiner kuuk min caarco kan̰ Lebi kat siy ko *dokkanne, kar gee ku Israyeel gay aaɗaag gay satkiner kaak ŋu koliy *Lebi. Ya ŋuur kat siy ko satkiner-ak, maa di pey gin pey *mee satkiner ka pey kaak ar *Melkidenez? Ka seener gay, ŋa pey gin pey satkiner ka pey kaak ŋu koliy *Haruun.
Asaan gii imilin̰ gay satkiner min ɗo *ger ka Buŋdi. Ŋaar-ak imilin̰ gaanuun ka Muusa oki.
Ka seener, ɗo kaawin kuuk Iisa kaawtu pa-ak, ŋa newsiig gemo a ŋaa goye ar wer kaak ŋu giniy *satkin ɗo Buŋdi. Kar min aginiyji daarin̰ gay, ginno gem kaak yaa un̰je wer kaak ŋu giniy satkin ɗo Buŋdi.
Asaan gee-ak iban tam kadar Rabbinte Buŋ amil min Zuude ho ŋaar sa tatik ko min Zuude. Iŋ taar-at ko, Muusa bal kaawe bat ɗo gee ku tamba ta gay satkiner.
Yampa, maan kaak as pey pakgigɗo pey maan kaak pey yaa bayne pey *mee satkiner ka pey kaak ar *Melkidine.
Ŋaar-ak ginno asaan *gaanuun kaak Buŋ bertu botol ɗo geemir. Ŋa gaarig iŋ gudurre taat bera goye ka gaasɗo.
Ka seener gay, kaaw ɗo Kitamner ŋu kaaw aman: " Kiŋ goy *mee satkiner doo ar gay satkiner kaak ŋu gintu ar Melsi-Seetanne. "
Nu taliy-aŋ rasgitɗo, asaan uudin taat ta raɗaw wala daaɗ di-ak ko, nu iciit uŋti.
Asaan *gaanuun ka Muusa bal nigeŋ ko maan kaak kaawa. Kar ba aaro, Buŋ gintu niyine a gii gase botol taat ŋaa obin̰ji. Iŋ taar-at ko oki, gii gasin̰ botol taat gi ɓaawe uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ togiltu pey ɗo gay satkiner ho Buŋ sa togiltu iŋ *satkiner.
Ɗo bi ka Iisa gay, *Yuudinna ginno pey *mee satkiner asaan Buŋ ɗiytu aman: " *Rabbine togil ko ho ŋa ibanno pey tak-tak. Kiŋ goy gay satkiner doo. "
Ansii ko, koɗok di, Iisa oki weeyig adiy ka gusuurdi.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gay satkiner dakina ku pey astu, asaan muutco sa toɗco.
Kar Iisa gay goy doo, asaan ŋaar goy doo doo. Iŋ taar-at ko, gee yaa gine gay satkiner ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Ampa-ak, Buŋ gin gudurre taat bera goye doo ɗo gee kuuk asa min ɗo darrey. Ŋa goy doo ɗo uŋco ka geemir a ŋuu tale baaco kaƴco.
Ampa-ak, siŋ ku Iisa kat berte pey *mee satkiner ka tatko kaak ar ŋaar-aŋka. Ŋaar gemno. Ŋaar gemno tak-tak iŋ kaay. Ŋaar gay, ŋu doɓtu serek min ɗo gay zunuubinnar ho Buŋ, ŋaar pakgig serek min kuwa ka samaaner.
Iŋ taar-at ko, agindaw ku gay satkiner kat siyga. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Iisa bal gine riy taar-an di, ŋa beriy *satkine ja ɗo uŋco ka geemir, kar ba aar gay, ŋa beriy satkine ɗo bi ka zunuubinna ku geemir. Sando, ŋaar kat gin ko riy-anta, asaan uudin taat ŋa gintu pa-ak, ŋaar mattu ko.
Ka seener gay, *gaanuun ka Muusa kaawtu a ŋuu diyin̰ gee kuuk ginaag agindaw ku gay satkiner, asaan ŋuur gin koogin kuuk raɗaw. Kar kaaw taat Buŋ togiltu iŋ *gaanuun-ak gay, taar as ɗo nun Roŋji ka Buŋdi, ŋaar goy doo.
Iŋ kaawin kuuk ni kaawiiko-aŋku oki, ooyit kaawor-anta: ni gin mee satkiner ka tatko-aŋ di ho ŋa goy ɗo meeday ta sees ka Sultan kaak tatiko ka Buŋ ka kuwa ka samaaner.
Min ŋaar-ak, ŋa giniit sawa di ɗo Buŋdi. Ŋaar gay riyor kaak taɓ kaak Buŋ doɓtu ho kaak bera botol ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ho ŋaar di *Rabbin Buŋ di siyig wer ka seener.
Ka seener gay, ay *mee satkiner ka tatko goy ɗo wer kaak ŋaa gine *satkin ɗo Buŋdi ho ŋaa gine *satkin ɗo Buŋdi. Paa ko, min ɗo tan̰ji-at, ŋaar ginno pey maan kaak yaaji iye satkine.
Ka seener gay, Iisa Masi goy ko ɗo kiɗar, kar gay satkiner yaa goye pey weriy tak-tak. Paa ko, gee kuuk giniy satkine-ak yaa gine gay satkine ho ŋuu gine gay satkine.
Uudin taat gee-ak giniy satkine, ŋuur karmiyaag Buŋ iŋ margico. Sando, ŋuur-ak gina ar margico taat Buŋ bertu izinne. Nabi Muusa siytu botol taat ŋaa siyin *ger ka Buŋdi ar taat ŋa gaariiji. Uudin taat ŋa gaariiji-at, taar-at sawa-sawa. Iŋ taar-at ko, gee ku Israyeel giniy satkine ar margico kaak Buŋ gaariiji-aka.
Ansii ko, Muusa gin pey riy ta pey uŋda. Kar ba aaro, ŋa gin pey *Jamaw ta marbinto. Pa-ak gay, ŋu gaara kadar kaawin kuuk Buŋ kaawtu a ŋuu obe miirir-ak yaa goye pey ɗo kaay.
Ka seener, ya kaaw taat awalle-at kat bal ween̰ji di-ak, zer Buŋ yaa bariye pey wer ka seeriŋkar walla?
Kar Buŋ gay poocit kaawco ɗo gee ku Israyeel ho ɗo gee ku Zuuda, ŋa kaawtu aman: " Wiktin asaw, ka seener, *Rabbin kaaw aman: ‟ Nun naa gine *Jamaw ta marbinto iŋ gee ku Israyeel ho iŋ gee ku Zuuda oki.
Ŋaar-ak arro taat nu obit awalle iŋ aginiyco ƴiriy taat nu obtu awalle wiktin taat nu obtu pisin̰co a naa imilin̰co min kiɗ ka Meser. Ŋu bal karmiyin kaawor-ata. Sando, nun sa bal ooye iŋ ŋuura, ka seener, Rabbin ɗiytu.
asaan ŋaar-aŋ ko *Jamaw ta pey taat naa obin̰ gee ku Israyeel min wiktin taat gamin-ak yaa ase. An ko kaaw taat Rabbin kaawtu: ‟ Naa un̰jin̰ gaanuun-ak ɗo aditco ho naa siirin̰ ɗo aditco. Naa kuuniye ar Buŋco ho ŋuur oki yaa kuuniye ar nunu. "
Kar ay gemo, ŋu ɓildaagɗo pey geemir ho ay gem di ɓildaagɗo siŋji ka geemir. Ŋu kaawiy pey aman: ‟ Ki ibingig Rabbiner. Okin̰co, ŋuu ibininno min ɗo kapak yoo kaak tatik paka. "
asaan naa tale amindawco ɗo bi ka zunuubinnico ho naa rawtinno pey zunuubinnico tak-tak. " "
Ŋa kaawtu pey aman: " Yaman, Buŋ togiltu gemo ar gemo kuuk awalle-aku. Yampa gemo-ak, ŋu zaɓ ko ho koɗok di ŋuu zooɗe. "
Ku iban tam kadar awalle gee ku Israyeel gin botol taat ŋuu abdiye Buŋ ɗo duniiner.
Ka seener gay, ŋu siytu ger ka Buŋdi. Ɗo ger-ak, ŋu siytu portikaw taat ŋu koliy " *cawar." Ɗo wer-ak ko, ŋu biƴtu lampa rakki, ŋu siytu jarɗaɗ ho ŋu siytu mappa kaak ŋu ɗuuniig mappa ho ŋu siytu kuwa. Kar pey, ŋu siytu ger ka seeriŋkar, ŋu siytu atta ho ŋu kaawtu aman: " Wer ka Buŋdi."
Ɗo wer-ak, ŋa gin *kordindi rakki taat ŋu giniy *satkine. Ɗo wer-ak gay, ŋa gin *kordindi taat ŋu siytu ɗo *ger ka Buŋdi ho ŋu ɗuunit okintiti iŋ daabne. Ɗo ɗatik ta zimilla-ak gay, ŋa gin maan kaak ŋu koliy *Haruun kaak *cawar aale ho iŋ maktumne ta marbinto kuuk ŋu siirtu awalle.
Min ŋaar-ak, nu taliig kerubim rakki kaak gooƴaat portikuwti ɗo wer-aka. Kar diŋ gay, ni gedarro kaawe sooɗa.
Hiyya, gamin-ak kuuk ŋu siytu pa-ak, kar uŋda, agindaw ku gay satkiner teestu gine riyoy ɗo uŋco ka ger ka Buŋdi ar kaak awalle-aka. Ho ɗo wer-ak ko, agindaw ku gay satkiner giniy riy ta salkiye.
Ka seeriŋkar gay, ŋa un̰jitu pey ɗo ger ka tatko ho ɗo uŋji ka pey, ar ŋaar di mee satkiner ka tatko di. Iŋ taar-at oki, *mee satkiner ka tatko ginno botol taat ŋaa bere *satkine ɗo bi ka meen̰ji ho ɗo bi ka gee kuuk ibanno Buŋ.
Sando, Ruwwin ta Buŋdi gaayiitit kaawoy aman: ‟ Di ŋaar-ak, giico toɗe botol taat ŋuu gine botol taat ŋuu gine *cawar ɗo Buŋdi. Asaan wer kaak awalle-ak, ŋuur goy misa pey ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Buŋ kaawiico pey ɗo daŋlay. Kar ɗo wiktin taar-at gay, Buŋ toɗco. Gamin kuuk ŋu giniy *satkin ɗo Buŋdi ho iŋ gamin kuuk ŋu giniy satkine oki, ansi-ak, gem kaak abdiya Buŋ gediraaɗo ŋaa gine sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Ya ɗo teendi di, ŋu tiya tee, ŋu siya tee ho ŋu siya tee ho ŋu ooy *batiziygu iŋ gamin dakina kuuk ar aariɗ kaak Buŋ rakiyo. Aariɗna-ak gaara kadar ŋu gina jookumo ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi nam ƴiriy taat Buŋ asiy newse duniine.
Kar gay, Masi gay as *mee satkiner ka tatko ka aginiyte kaak samaane kuuk samaane. Ŋa goy ɗo *ger ka Buŋdi iŋ tarram kaak pakgigɗo ho pakgigɗo pakgig ja tak-tak. Taar-an gay, ŋaar geenno min gamin ku duniiner-aŋku.
Ŋa un̰jitu pey ɗo wer ka Buŋdi-aka. Ŋa bal un̰je iŋ baar ku ammaamnar, wala iŋ roŋ ku ammaamnar, wala iŋ baar ku ammaamnar. Min ŋa un̰je-ak, Iisa un̰jitu pey uŋda sooɗa, ŋaa gase jile ka gaasɗo.
Ka seener gay, baar ku kumnar, ku pooɗikdi ho iŋ leegin kuuk ŋu ɗuunit maasoy-ak, ŋuur kuuk nigaag ziŋkico samaane ho kuuk gin *satkine oki ginaag ziŋkico n̰aaɗa ŋuu goye *cawar ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Min ŋaar-ak, ba aaro, ba aaro, baar ku Masi! Ŋaar meen̰ji Buŋ bertu *satkin ɗo meen̰ji iŋ Ruwwin ta Buŋdi. Ruwwin-at baati sa, ŋaar meen̰ji sa gaara kadar baar ku Masi-ak yaa saamiye aditko min ɗo gamin kuuk samaanno kuuk mate. Paa kat, kuu gine botol taat ya kuu abdiye Buŋ kaak goy mento.
Ansii ko, Iisa Masi gin pey ɗatik ta marbinto. Ansii kat, gee kuuk ŋu koliig Buŋ asiy gase haginey taat ŋa kaawtu a ŋuu goye doo ɗo uŋji ka awalle. Ampaa ko, muutco asiy gase botol taat ŋuu gase pey haginey taat Buŋ kaawtu a ŋuu gase goye ka gaasɗo.
Cokiyoŋ, ya gem kaak gin portikaw, ŋaar mate. Yampa, ya gem kaak gin portikaw-ak, ŋaar isgigɗo tak-tak.
Ka seener gay, ya gem kaak obit kaaw-at, ta gediraaɗo yaa gine portiko wiktin taat ŋa goyiy mento.
Kar gay, ya gem looga iŋ baarir sa, Buŋ toɗcoɗo.
Ŋu kaawiy pa-ak, asaan Yuudinna okin̰co ictu kaaw taat *gaanuun ka Muusa kaawtu okin̰ji ɗo *gaanuun. Min ŋa kaawtu pa-ak, ŋa ictu baar, ŋa ɗuuniit baar, ŋa ɗuuniit ɗew ta kooginar iŋ amay ho ŋa ɗuuniit itir ɗo maktumne-ata. Kar ŋa kockiciit pey ɗo gee okin̰co.
ho ŋa ɗiytu aman: " Ŋuur-aŋ baarir. Baar-aŋ ɗuunit *Jamaw ta marbinto taat Buŋ kaawiiko a ŋuu ase iŋ uŋji.
Kar ŋa ɗukumiico pey baarco ar kaak ŋu ɗuuniig *ger ka Buŋdi-aka ho iŋ gamin okin̰co kuuk ŋu giniy satkine.
Kar gamin okin̰co kuuk iŋ baar-ak gay, *gaanuun kaawa a ŋuu goye *cawar ay gemo uudin taat ŋuu kuuniye. Kar wer kaak gee bal ooye baarir-ak, Buŋ saamiyaajiɗo maanna. "
Ka seener, kaawin kuuk gaara ar maan kaak goy ka samaaner-ak, taar-an di gedirgiy gase botol taat ŋuu gine *cawar. Kar gay, ka seener, ŋuur kuuk goy ka samaaner-ak, ŋu giniy satkine ar kaak ŋu giniy satkine.
Ka seener gay, Masi kaak Buŋ doɓtu-ak, ŋaar un̰jituɗo ka seener. Ŋaar asɗo tak-tak kuwa ka seener. Kar gay, ŋaar un̰jitu-ak kuwa ka samaaner di, asaan diŋ gay, ŋaa bayne uŋte ka Buŋdi uŋte.
Ŋaar-ak gay, mee satkiner ka tatko un̰jitu atta ɗo ger ka Buŋdi-aka, illa ŋa un̰jitu iŋ baar ku gemor di iŋ baar ku gemor.
Ɗo bi ka meen̰ji, Buŋ iban kadar min Buŋ kilgiyit duniine, ŋa taaɓiyig ko taaɓiye dakina. Kar gay, ɗo wiktin taat duniin gaaye, Iisa Masi yaa gaare ziy dakina a ŋaa gine saamiye ka zunuubinnico. Ampaa ko, iŋ meen̰ji ŋa giniy *satkine.
Ya muut ta geemir-ak, muutco yaa gine ar taar-at di uŋco. Kar ba aar gay, seriin ta Buŋdi asiy ɗukume seriine.
Ansii ko, Iisa Masi oki, ŋaar mattu rakki di ŋaa icin zunuubinna ku gee dakina a ŋaa icin̰co. Kar ka seeriŋkar gay, ŋa asaaco gaare zunuubinna okin̰co ɗo ŋuur kuuk ooma a ŋuu gase jile.
Ka seener gay, gaanuun kaak Buŋ kaawtu-ak, ŋaar goy ko gondiko ɗo gamin kuuk samaane kuuk yaa ase. Kar gay, ŋaar ginno baati ta gamin kuuk goy diŋka-aŋ di. Iŋ gamin ŋuur-ak di, gamin kuuk ŋu giniy satkine ar ŋuur-aŋku. Paa ko, ŋu gediraaɗo pey ŋuu gine *cawar ɗo gee kuuk goy anne.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, min awalle, ŋu wakila di koocin̰ *satkin-at ɗo uŋco ka geemir. Asaan satkin-at sa, ŋu gedarro pey ozilin̰co. Iŋ taar-at oki, ŋu ibanno kadar ŋu gin zunuubinna tak-tak ɗo uŋco ka geemir.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gee liya pey maan kaak ŋu saamiyiig zunuubinnico rakki di.
Ka seener gay, baar ku ammaamnar iŋ ku ammaamnar, ŋuur saamiya zunuubinna min ɗo uŋco.
Min Iisa as ɗo duniiner, ŋa kaawtu ɗo Kitamner aman: ‟ Nu rakaaɗo satkine ho *satkin ɗo Buŋdi. Kar gay, nu rakaaɗo zir, nu rakaaɗo satkine.
Ɗo bi ka zunuubinnar-ak, ŋa bal nige tak-tak zunuubinna ho ziy sa sooɗa.
Hiyya, nu telkiiji aman: ‟ Di ŋaar-ak, nun as ko, nun Buŋdi, nu ginit ko riy taat ki rakiyo. " Min ŋaar-ak, nu siirtu ɗo bi kanto ko ɗo Kitamner a naa gine taat ki rakiyo. "
Min ŋa kaawtu pey aman: ‟ Nu bal rake ho ki bal ooye ɗo gamin kuuk ŋu giniy *satkine. Nu bal ooye ɗo gamin kuuk ŋu giniy satkine, ŋuur kuuk ŋu giniy satkine, ŋuur kuuk ŋu oriy satkine ho kuuk ŋu giniy zunuubinna. Nu bal ooye ho ki bal ooye ɗo gamin-aŋku. "
ho ŋa kaawtu aman: " Nun ozilinte. Waan kaak awalle-ak, ŋaa icin̰ji ar kaak ki rakiyo. Kar ba aaro, ŋaa icin̰ kaak awalle-aka, kar ŋaa gasin̰ ka seeriŋkar. "
Buŋ gintu pa-ak ar taat Buŋ rakiyo, ho iŋ taar-at ko, Buŋ doɓtu loko iŋ *satkin taat ŋu beriig zi ka Iisa Masi doo.
Kun kawta, gay satkiner rakki pey goya ho ŋa gina riy satkine. Satkin-at gay, ŋu giniy satkine ho ŋu giniy satkine dakina ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Satkin-at gay gedarro imilin̰ zunuubinna tak-tak.
Kar Iisa gay, wiktin taat ŋa bertu *satkin rakki ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, ŋa beriico satkine rakki ɗo bi ka zunuubinnar ho diŋ gay, ŋa goy ɗo meeday.
Kar ba aar, ŋa goy pey ɗo wer kaak ŋaaco gedire ɗo adiney, ŋuu gine wer ka lee asin̰ji.
Ka seener gay, ta negindaw paa di ŋaaco gaare ziŋkico ɗo gee kuuk Buŋ doɓtu.
Ruwwin ta Buŋdi sa gaaraako pey kadar maanna-ak kaawa seene ɗo bi kaŋko.
" An ko *Jamaw ta pey taat naa amile iŋ ŋuura min ɗo menaw ŋuur-ak, ka seener, Rabbin ɗiy aman: ‟ An ko kaaw taat naaco gaare *gaanuun-ak ɗo aditco ho naa siire ɗo kaƴco. "
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, nu asiy rawtinno pey zunuubinnico iŋ zunuubinnico okin̰co kuuk samaanno ŋu giniyo. " "
Kar ɗo wer kaak Buŋ saamiyiig zunuubinna-aŋ gay, ginno pey *satkin taat ŋuu gine pey zunuubinna.
Ampa-ak, gem kol siŋtay, kaawkoŋ bombo, kuu goye bombo ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi iŋ baar ku Iisa Masi.
Ŋa gaarinti botol taat sooɗ-sooɗ a nii gase goye ka gaasɗo. Taar-an gay, taar ko iŋ ziy ka Iisa.
Ɗo wer-ak, ŋa gin gay satkiner dakina kuuk goy ɗo *ger ka Buŋdi.
Nu ɓaayiy iŋ gelbin kaak taɓ ho iŋ imaan taat samaane ɗo Buŋdi. Iŋ gelbin kaak samaane kuuk ŋu imiliit pikirre taat samaanno min ɗo aditco kuuk gallo ho iŋ amay kuuk samaane kuuk ŋu acciig ziŋkini.
Kar gay, ya ni ooy iŋ imaan taat ni kaawtu, diŋ gay, ni obiit kat imaan ɗo Buŋdi.
Ya gi goyiy misa iŋ gelbin rakki, gi ɓagguwoŋ ziŋkiko a gi ɓaa gine elgin rakki ho gii gine gamin kuuk samaane.
Ya ku ɓaawaw ɗo geray ku salaaner, dakoŋ rasenno ziŋkiko ar taat gee ku salaaner ɓaggiyo. Indoŋ Buŋ iŋ gelbinko. Ka seener gay, maan ka pey kuuniya diŋka asa ko moota.
Ka seener gay, min ni gastu botol ta seener ho ni gastu botol taat ŋuu ibinin̰ seen ta Buŋdi. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ginno pey satkine taat ŋuu gine pey asaan ni ginno zunuubinna.
Ŋaar-ak kolaw kat yaaco ɗukume seriine ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ho ŋuur kuuk ooma yaaco ase ɗo uŋco ka gee kuuk oomaagu, ŋuu orin̰ ako.
" Kiŋ newsiig gaanuun ka Muusa. Ya ŋu bal deen kaawoy, kaawco mataaɗo illa ya kaawin subba di yaa obin̰ maanna.
Ku pakira maa di ɗo gaaƴiƴko ar kaak Roŋ ka Buŋdi paayaaga? Ku iban tam kadar baar kuuk *Jamaw ta marbinto iyiig iŋ ŋuura, ŋuur kuuk Buŋ asiy gine *cawar ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Kar Ruwwin ta barkin ta Buŋdi gay, berkiico pey a ŋuu goye keɗer iŋ uŋco.
Asaan ni iban kaaw taat ŋa kaawtu aman: ‟ Ya nu ɗukume seriine, nun meendu naa kappiyen di ɗo kaay. " Ho ŋa kaaw pey aman: " Rabbin Buŋ yaa ɗukume seriine ɗo geen̰ji. "
Ŋaar-ak ginno kolaw ɗo pisin̰ji ku Buŋ kaak goy mento.
Moyoŋ ɗo gamin kuuk awalle kuuk goy awalle. Ɗo wiktin taar-at ko, ku gas taaɓin dakina iŋ taaɓin dakina.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gee taliig ŋu ajimiyaagu. Ŋu taaɓiyaagu ɗo uŋco ka geemir. Kar daarin̰ gay, ŋu aaƴiig iŋ gee kuuk jookumo ho isgigɗo iŋ ŋuura.
Asaan ku taaɓiyaako samaane ɗo gee kuuk goy daŋaayne ho ya ŋu sokig gaminko iŋ galal, ku ooyiig iŋ gelbin rakki. Ka seener gay, ku iban kadar goyin̰co samaane, ŋuur kuuk goy misa iŋ kuŋko oki.
Dakoŋ rasenno gurusko ku maaniiko, asaan ŋaar-ak gasit ko hagin taat dakina yaaji kappiye.
Goyoŋ bombo, kuu gedire taaɓiye, asaan ya ku gina taat Buŋ rakiyo, kuu gase haginey kaak ŋa kaawtu a ŋaaji bere.
Asaan ɗo wiktin taat naa ase-ak, Buŋ yaa ase koɗok di, ŋaa taaye tak-tak.
Kar ŋaar kaak sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi-ak gay, ŋaar yaa gase iŋ imaanco, kar ŋaa goye pey. Ho ya ŋaar kaak sellen̰ pakgigɗo, nun rawtaagɗo tak-tak. "
Kuŋ gay, ni iban kadar kuŋ kat *paliinnaɗo, yampa-ak, ŋaar niggigɗo maanna. Kar gay, ya ku aamin ɗo Iisa Masi, ŋaar kat yaa jile goyin̰co ku geemir.
Ansii ko, imaan, ŋaar goy iŋ gamin kuuk gi hariya a gamin kuuk gi eriyo, kar gay, ŋaar aamine ɗo gamin kuuk gi talgigɗo misa.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, aginiyji ku Yuudinnar kaawco kaawco a ŋuuco kaawe seene.
Ampa-ak, ni pakira kadar kaaw ta Buŋdi, taar goy doo, ni obiit kaawoy bombo, yampa-ak, ni pakirigɗo gamin kuuk cigile min ɗo gamin kuuk ni taltu.
Ɗo bi ka *Kayin ko, Abeel bertu satkine. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ŋa gaariico kadar ŋa gem sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ho Buŋ sa kaawji seene. Sando, iŋ taar-at ko, ŋa mattu.
Ɗo bi ka Enook, Buŋ ƴiimig ŋaar-ak uudin taat ŋu mataaɗo. Ŋa bal goye pey ɗo maginer, asaan Buŋ ƴiimig ŋaar-ak. Ka seener, min Buŋ bal ƴiimin̰ji, ŋaar gala.
Kar ya waan ginno imaan gay, gi gediraaɗo ŋaaco ooye Buŋ, asaan ŋa pakira kadar maan kaak Buŋ yaa gine, ŋa goy iŋ odinay ho ŋa beraag haginco ɗo ŋuur kuuk bariyaaga.
Nowe gay, iŋ imaanko-at, Buŋ gaariijig gamin kuuk ŋa bal talin̰ gamin kuuk cigile ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ŋa karmiyiig ɗo Buŋdi ho ŋa siytu markaba taat ŋaa jilin̰ geen̰ji iŋ geen̰ji okin̰co. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ŋa kaawtu kadar gee ku duniiner okin̰co jookumo. Ho iŋ imaanco-at ko, ŋa darjiyiig a ŋa goy sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Min ŋaar-ak, koɗok di Ibraayim koliiga. Ŋa ictu niyine a ŋaa ɗeete ɗo wer kaak ŋaaji berin haginey. Kar ŋa ɗeettu. Ŋa ɗeettu, ŋa ibanno wer kaak ŋa ɓaayiyo.
Min ŋaar-ak, iŋ imaanco, ŋa goytu ɗo kiɗ kaak Buŋ kaawiiji ɗo Ibraayim a ŋaa goye ɗo darre taat ŋa kaawtu awalle. Ŋa goytu ɗo geray. Isaaka iŋ Yakuub oki, ŋuur ko kuuk asa goye sawa iŋ ŋuura, kar iŋ ŋuura oki, ŋu goytu ɗo Yakuub.
Asaan Buŋ iban kadar geeger-ak, ŋaar ko kaak pinig geeger kaak Buŋ di pinig samaane. Ŋaar ko gay pinindi ho ŋa kilgiyig samaane.
Ɗo imaanco ko, Ibraayim obiit gudurre taat ŋaa wee mico. Taar oki zaɓ ko tak-tak. Iŋ amaanne oki, ta obtu gudurre taat Buŋ kaawiitit ɗo geemir.
Ampaa ko, min gem rakki di-ak di, ŋu weeyig wee ka marbinto. Gee-ak ar kaalnal kuuk goy ka samaaner, ŋu paka puk-puk ar markab kaak ginno min ɗo pisin̰ji di.
Gee-ak okin̰co mattu iŋ imaanco, asaan ŋu bal gasin̰ maan kaak Buŋ kaawtu a ŋaaco kaawe ɗo geemir-aka. Kar gay, ŋu talig iŋ odinco, ŋu ooyiita ho ŋu kaawtu ɗo geemir a ŋu goy martaw ho martico di.
